    <string name="about_desc">Sukun helps you pray without distraction — automatically silencing your phone at prayer times and restoring it right after.</string>
    <string name="key_features">Key Features</string>
    <string name="features_list">• Automatic prayer times based on your location.\n• Precise background silencing using exact alarms.\n• Manual silence for focus sessions anytime.\n• Centralized volume dashboard (Media &amp; Ringer).</string>
    <string name="how_it_works_title">How it Works</string>
    <string name="how_it_works_desc">Sukun schedules an alarm for each prayer. When it arrives, it saves your volume, enters Do Not Disturb, and mutes your phone. Once done, everything is restored exactly as it was.</string>
